name: Glory Games Standard Presale NFT Pass

metadata.name: Premium Presale NFT Pass
metadata.description: The best rewards pass for entry into Glory Games metaverse. This ticket entitles you to mint a Gen 0 Pet NFT (only Gen 0 pets have unlimited breeding) and an avatar, first in the queue. Premium ticket holders also qualify for other open airdrops and entitlements, as OG roles. Probably the best chance to score Glory Games NFTs.
